chapters.name: Chapter 43 - 43: Who is the better Swordsman

name: Reincarnated as an Elf Prince
summary: Did I seriously reincarnate as a prince..?Felix was reincarnated as Lindarion Sunblade, a prince of Eldorath, destined for greatnessor so they say. In a world where magic and swordsmanship rule. True power is everything, and the strong shape history. But strength isnt given, its earned. With a System awakening within him, one that pushes his limits with deadly quests sometimes, helps him with skills, he refuses to be just another noble in a gilded cage.Trials await, enemies lurk in the shadows, and even among his own kind, power breeds conflict.But he will rise. Not just as a princebut as a ruler, a warrior, and a legend over the entire world.
author: BeMyMoon
